80 columns max, _NEVER_ more. Try to keep functions under 30 lines.

8 space tabs

class names start with

common variable names:

i,j,k	- indices 
x,y,z	- unknowns  (math)
a,b,c	- constants (math)

fn 	- file name
f	- file object

src	- source
dst	- destination

K&R style names (lower case, underscore delimited)

macros - trailing underscore (macro_name_)

costants - upper case (CONSTANT_X)

- try to keep identifiers under 20 characters

